<h1>Reasoning Model Cost Guide</h1><p class="updated" style="color:#6B7689;font-size:14px;margin-top:-6px">Updated 12 July 2026 · first published 4 July 2026</p>
<p>Reasoning models like o3, o4-mini, DeepSeek-R1, QwQ, and MiMo generate internal "thinking" tokens before producing output. This hidden cost can inflate your bill 5-30x. This guide breaks down when reasoning models are worth the premium and when a standard model is the smarter spend.</p>

<div class="hero-stats">
  <div class="hero-stat"><span class="num">5-30x</span><span class="lbl">Cost multiplier</span></div>
  <div class="hero-stat"><span class="num">8</span><span class="lbl">Models compared</span></div>
